sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuario
    participant M as CreateFolderModal
    participant H as useTreeData
    participant A as API
    participant B as Backend
    
    U->>M: Click New Folder
    U->>M: Ingresa nombre
    U->>M: Click Create
    M->>H: createFolder(name)
    H->>A: POST /api/files/create
    A->>B: HTTP POST
    B->>B: Crear carpeta
    B-->>A: Response
    A-->>H: Data
    H-->>U: Actualizar árbol